```plantuml
@startuml nightingaleproject_Reference-Client

actor User
participant "React UI" as UI
participant "RecordController" as RC
participant "TimedHostedService" as THS
participant "NVSS API" as NVSS
participant "Database" as DB

User -> UI: Upload VRDR Record
UI -> RC: POST /api/records
RC -> DB: Save Record
RC -> THS: Notify new record

THS -> DB: Retrieve new records
THS -> NVSS: Submit VRDR Message
loop Acknowledgement & Retry
    NVSS -> THS: Acknowledge Message
    THS -> DB: Update Record Status
    THS -> NVSS: Retry if no ack
end
THS -> DB: Store Response

User -> UI: Check message status
UI -> RC: GET /api/records/status
RC -> DB: Retrieve Record Status
RC -> UI: Return Status

@enduml
```